<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>84</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hansie him umlo, Pathien Belam No
 Lalchutphah chu a um zan a um puoi;
 Thaumei vak leh nisa ngailo,
 Lal Pathien tawh kumkhaw sawtin vaihawm un au.

[V2]
 Amen, hung mai ta'n aw, Lalpa Isu,
 Lalpa Isun ei hehpihna chu;
 Mi thiengtho te kawm achun um hen,
 Hallelujah Amen, Hallelujah Amen.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa thiemgaute thagau Pathien chun,
 Thil hung tung pai dingte chu etsakin;
 Ngaitie, hung kit vak ding ka hi,&quot;
 Thu kigen masa awi chu a nau vak ina.

[V4]
 3. A phat hungtung ding ahi ta ngala,
 Kituplo chu kituplo in um hen;
 Mithiengtho chu hih thiengtho in,
 Aw hung um zel henla, hung kit vak ding ka hi.

[V5]
 4. Hilh masak thu hi mi'n a lak mang chun,
 Hinna thing leh khaw thiengtho a a chan;
 Chu Pathien in la mang ina,
 Zie thu hetsakpa hin &quot;Hung kit pai ding ka hi.</lyrics>
<title>Amen, Hungmai Ta Uo!</title>
</song>